    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/luwei10000/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u51436662-60.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/luwei10000/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">翩翩</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-10-31"
      class="main-meta">2013-10-31 01:06:13</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6364352_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  记得大二的时候学政治学原理，老师让我们背整整一本的《政治学基础》，那是本非常“马克思”的教材。不过不得不说那里面对“权力”的定义是很严谨的：  ……政治权力实际上是在特定的力量对比关系中，政治权力主体为了实现和维护自身的利益而拥有的对政治权力客体的制约能力。...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6364352_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6364352_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评21篇
                </a>
